txt.en: Destroyed White Hand supplies in Drû Vádokan ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
The White Hand encampment is stocked with crates of supplies from Orthanc and would be crippled if they were to be destroyed.

You have encountered crates of vile tools and disgusting Orc-rations in the White Hand encampment. Without these crucial supplies from Isengard, the Orc-forces of Wildermore would be crippled.\n\nIf you were to destroy these supplies, the White Hand's grip on the Balewood would slip greatly.
You have destroyed many crates of vital supplies and crippled the White Hand's assault in the Balewood. The Orcs of Isengard will now find mounting assaults into Wildermore far more challenging.
Destroy White Hand supplies in Drû Vádokan ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Crates of White Hand supplies can be found throughout Drû Vádokan in north-west Balewood.\n\nYou should destroy crates of the White Hand in an effort to cripple their assaults into Wildermore.
You have destroyed many crates of supplies and crippled the White Hand's assault in the Balewood.
